fields.agent_remarks: Nobody wants to miss out on their dream home. Buying and selling in one move can be stressful, costly, and inconvenient. Here’s a quote from Homeward so you can buy 1250 S Capital of Texas Hwy, Austin, TX 78746, USA before you sell with a winning all-cash, non-contingent offer. Peace.

fields.bio: I'm an avid tennis player, I love the outdoors, and I'm excited to tell people about buying with cash!

I was born and raised in central Texas. I have an extensive background in the real estate industry ranging from transaction coordination to a top producing agent.In every situation  treat customers the way I would want to be treated. I am in the process of completing my bachelors degree in business administration as well as raising two amazing children. I am always happy to help so feel free to contact me any time.

I have been in the real estate profession since 2003. My passion is helping Buyers find their new home and to make the transaction stress free and exciting. Thank you for the opportunity to assist you in this process.
I'm an avid tennis player, I love the outdoors, and I'm excited to tell people about buying with cash!
I'm passionate about all things real estate! I joined Homeward in 2020 to help people buy before they sell, and haven't looked back.
I’ve been with Homeward since 2019, am an avid tennis player, and last month broke our company record by helping more than 20 customers buy before they sell!
I’ve been with Homeward since 2019, I enjoy true-crime mystery books, and last month broke our company record for the number of customers I helped buy before they sold!
